tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE charging_patterns (
   charging_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   vehicle_id INT,
   start_time TIMESTAMP,
   end_time TIMESTAMP,
   energy_consumed DECIMAL,
   grid_impact_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id INT,
    vehicle_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    energy_usage DECIMAL,
    FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES charging_stations(station_id)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
  station_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  capacity DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model VARCHAR(255),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  owner_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE owners (
  owner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  email VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE grid_impact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_id INT,
  impact_level VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
